from spacy_conllu import main as spacy_main

This are the funcitons I have:

- spacy_main(infile, outfile, num): analyses first #num sentences in infile and prints the output in the outfile file
- clean_text(content): cleans the text according to certain parameters
- deanotate(inflie, outfile, num): deanotates the sentences from a conllu file, returning them


- test_annotation(annotation1, annotation2, num, attribute="upos", printf=0): compares two annotations

